Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 是tera suck啊你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:16.50,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}tera 計算機容量的T(1024G）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看見你飛起來的時候 我對你有多麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.42,0:18:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不止是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別的超頻連接者們也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(410,430)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.64,0:18:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.91,0:18:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是問你在哪裏潛入的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.43,0:18:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲州街道 我坐在公共汽車上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那趕緊把這場對戰結束掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.67,0:18:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接回家好好準備一下再到上面來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.56,0:18:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面就是無限制中立舞台啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.84,0:19:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要去哪裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經看到了吧 就是那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是舊東京塔？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,very yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.66,0:19:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,very yes啥的 去那種地方幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…就是那個…啥來著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是有個人想讓你見一見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說明白點 就是老子的家長啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家長？Ash的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他從對戰的第一線退下來已經很久了 所以你不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前被稱為鐵腕或者ICBM 被很多人畏懼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.22,0:19:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ICBM？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:37.50,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}ICBM:洲際彈道導彈（Intercontinental Ballistic Missile，縮寫ICBM）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個外號 就是伊卡洛斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.04,0:19:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個聽起來倒不是很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人啊 在你出現之前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.05,0:19:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是加速世界裏最接近天空的超頻連接者（Burst Linker）啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.43,0:20:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在在幹什麼呢？ Ash先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.17,0:20:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 本大爺現在正在等風停
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 來了 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 出發
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,hold me tight
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牆面垂行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Vertical Climb Drive>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.77,0:20:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了嗎 本大爺的牆面垂直行駛的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.54,0:20:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 之前你爬過大樓的牆壁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.27,0:20:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shit
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這風真是… Shit
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牢牢地Hold me tight
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了 根本聽不懂你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fly High
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.67,0:20:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 順利到達了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.53,0:20:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這輩子再也不坐輪胎少於四個的代步工具了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.43,0:20:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You真是什麼都不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.34,0:20:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機車的魅力正是由於會有翻車的風險
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個已經不是翻不翻車的問題了好不
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.82,0:21:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你也快下車
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.37,0:21:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人就是Ash先生的父輩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了 Ash
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.89,0:21:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你還沒有忘記我 我很欣慰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.86,0:21:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了 師父
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.52,0:21:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能忘記…這種事怎…怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.95,0:21:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說「Mega好久不見」了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.57,0:21:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是白銀之鴉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.57,0:21:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(453,430)}<Silver Crow>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.74,0:21:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.43,0:21:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.91,0:22:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面 我叫「Sky Raker」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.01,0:22:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}很高興見到你 鴉先生
